  <objective>At Luminescent we specialise in proprietary liquid-based isothermal heat engine technology, a disruptive innovation in the renewable energy sector. Our Lava heat engine is designed to harness a wide range of thermal energy from various industrial processes and turn it into a valuable commodity: electricity. This innovative approach not only elevates  the efficiency of industrial operations  but also contributes significantly to sustainability by generating clean, green power from untapped heat sources.</objective>
